&gt;&gt; This event is the first in a series focused on building baseline A=
I capabilities among users and top management teams of startups and busines=
ses=E2=80=94equipping them to lead effectively in an AI-powered world.<br>
&gt;&gt; The truth is that talented individuals and teams underuse today=E2=
=80=99s most popular AI tools=E2=80=94or use them incorrectly. This event w=
ill show you what=E2=80=99s possible when AI tools such as ChatGPT, Gemini,=
