 with purpose, skill, and impact in mind.<br>
&gt;&gt; Expect live demos, expert-led lectures, and workshops that highlig=
ht how the most popular AI tools transform how we work, communicate, and in=
novate. You will explore what =E2=80=9CAI-First=E2=80=9D really means and d=
iscover how TiE Ottawa and Carleton=E2=80=99s TIM program help
 professionals=E2=80=94and the broader community=E2=80=94harness AI to buil=
d solutions that matter.<br>
&gt;&gt; Whether you are launching a startup, growing a business, earning a=
 degree, or rethinking how to work smarter, this event will leave you inspi=
red, supported, and equipped to take the next step.<br>
